<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The Member States shall notify the Commission on a regular basis of the instances of behaviour referred to in Article 1 that have been discovered and shall provide it with all information regarding action taken by the administrative and/or judicial authorities. </inglise>
